ygData.messageBody:
Last nite was hunting At east Kanana with Trifrost for Craig Spider .

I had 1 bubble increase in ablut an hr,
We were doin it slowly with an Enchanter . I lure with my Shurikens , kill
and med up.
Tri manage to lvl to 17th.

The craig con Blue and Black to me, Yelow and red to Trufrost and his
friend. We kill Giffgawn sometimes. Lotsa Craig spiders and i'll be at E.K
for a while practising my skilling on trowing and Eagel Strike. And one is
welcome to join us. I'll proceed to PAw or Peramfrost in a couple og days.
Hopefully, Tri will be 18th then.I'll be backward lvling when I hit 21st Lvl
to 20th. anyone between 16th and 21st lvl can join us.

Yiyang at E.K
